10:23.333 --> 10:25.167
Sharon, what do you got?

10:25.167 --> 10:26.875
‐ Yeah, so,
I'm still working my way

10:26.875 --> 10:28.458
through the '98
internal budgets,

10:28.458 --> 10:32.625
but the sales rep bonus
structure incentivizes reps

10:32.625 --> 10:36.000
to push for higher doses
over longer periods of time.

10:36.000 --> 10:39.042
I don't think I've ever seen a
pharma company do that before.

10:39.042 --> 10:40.375
‐ Do you have management

10:40.375 --> 10:42.583
specifically pushing reps
to sell higher doses?

10:42.583 --> 10:44.458
‐ Not yet, but it is implied.

10:44.458 --> 10:46.167
‐ I don't need implied.
I need a direct link.

10:46.167 --> 10:47.542
I need examples that show

10:47.542 --> 10:50.208
reps dangerously pushing
higher doses for profit.

10:50.208 --> 10:52.875
‐ Well, we might find that
in the call notes.

10:52.875 --> 10:54.750
We just completed
cataloguing all of them,

10:54.750 --> 10:56.125
and a part of me thinks

10:56.125 --> 10:58.792
that there could be
some information in there.

10:58.792 --> 11:00.958
‐ I need orders
from management,

11:00.958 --> 11:02.875
not with the sales reps
or telling management.

11:02.875 --> 11:05.042
‐ Can I finish, Rick?

11:05.042 --> 11:08.167
We might find something
that leads us to a sales rep

11:08.167 --> 11:09.958
who's willing to flip
on the higher‐ups.

11:09.958 --> 11:11.500
‐ How?

11:11.500 --> 11:14.083
‐ These call notes contain
everything that they wrote

11:14.083 --> 11:18.208
to their managers
after every doctor's visit.

11:18.208 --> 11:21.708
So maybe there's a rep
that said people are

11:21.708 --> 11:24.292
getting addicted,
but they got ignored,

11:24.292 --> 11:27.292
and now they want
to talk about it.

11:27.292 --> 11:29.125
We might find a whistleblower.

11:29.125 --> 11:32.375
‐ Right, well,

11:32.375 --> 11:34.875
since we haven't found a
smoking gun in the higher‐ups,

11:34.875 --> 11:37.125
then whistleblower would be
our best bet, wouldn't it?

11:37.125 --> 11:39.042
‐ That is a wonderful idea,
boss,

11:39.042 --> 11:40.875
and I wish that I had had it.

11:40.875 --> 11:42.417
I.T. WORKER:
I can't believe you boys

11:42.417 --> 11:44.958
