for all of them.

12:02.500 --> 12:03.917
What's taken you months

12:03.917 --> 12:06.042
will now be accomplished
in just a few seconds.

12:06.042 --> 12:08.958
‐ Okay, well, let's get
the party started.

12:08.958 --> 12:14.792
