I'm lucky I'm alive.

58:17.000 --> 58:19.875
‐ I, um‐‐

58:19.875 --> 58:22.208
I promise,

58:22.208 --> 58:25.208
when I first came to you,

58:25.208 --> 58:27.375
I didn't know
